value.name: Contract farming - Wikipedia
value.snippet: Contract farming has to be commercially viable. To maximise profitability companies need to choose the best available farmers. Once suitable farmers have been identified it is then necessary to develop trust, as contracts will only work when both parties believe they are better off by engaging in them.

value.name: What is Custom Contract Growing and is it Right for You?

Having the landscape in place from the start makes good economic sense.
